reviews.review_text: 3-17-88 Good show. Another great remaster by C Miller.

Great mardi Gras show Volleyball, greenery, Lodghead was very drunk during Hamza El Din andcame up to me and yelled "Hey Shaun" and like 100 people stared it was so funny. John is so kind but he was a NY head and drunk in the middle of the Hamza El Din chant, and you could hear a pin drop, as such John was somewhat loud, I was vialing out and such, as such temember just don't drink
Enjoyable Spin Highlights:  Stuck Inside Of Mobile With The Memphis Blues Again (Bobby going for it, after a flub)
